“you might say it was a misdirection but you don’t usually misdirect on an arcane knowledge clue”

Personally, I read it (the plural clueing with a singular answer) as deliberate misdirection. But I don’t see whataboutism as being an arcane term, as its usage in popular discourse seems to have really taken off during the last ~10 years.

